<template>
    <section id="login" class="col-12 col-xl-10 mx-auto my-4">
      <input-form
        v-if="arrayInputs"
        :propArrayInputs="arrayInputs"
        v-on:validateInputs="validateInputs"
      />
    </section>
  </template>
  
  <script lang="ts">
    import { InputForms, TypeHelp } from "@/models/inputForms";
    import { Component, Prop, Vue } from "vue-property-decorator";
  
      
    @Component({})
      export class CodePrecifiqueForm extends Vue {
        @Prop() propArrayInputs!: InputForms[];

  data() {
    return {
      code: "",
      codeError: ""
    };
  }


  
    submitForm() {
      if (this.validateCode()) {
        alert("Código válido: " + this.code);
      } else {
        this.codeError = "O código deve conter de 1 a 4 dígitos.";
      }
    }

    validateCode() {
      const codeRegex = /^\d{1,4}$/;
      return codeRegex.test(this.code);
    }
  }
    export { CodePrecifiqueForm as default };
  </script>
  
  <style lang="scss" scoped></style>
